'''德克萨斯大学大河谷分校'''（{{lang-en|University of Texas Rio Grande Valley}}; 简称UTRGV）是一所位于[[德克薩斯州|德州]][[大河谷|大河谷]]的州立综合研究型大学，创办于2013年，由[[德州大学布朗思维尔分校|德州大学布朗思维尔分校]]（UT Brownsville）、[[德州大学泛美分校|德州大学泛美分校]]（UT Pan American）和[[德州大学哈灵根地方学术健康中心|德州大学哈灵根地方学术健康中心]]合并而成，于2015年全面投入運作。<ref>{{cite press release |first1=Jenny |last1=LaCoste-Caputo |first2=Karen |last2=Adler |url=http://utsystem.edu/news/2013/12/12/board-regents-votes-name-new-ut-south-texas-university-texas-rio-grande-valley |title=Board of Regents votes to name new UT in South Texas The University of Texas Rio Grande Valley |location=[[Austin,_Texas|Austin, Texas]] |publisher=The University of Texas System Office of Public Affairs |date=December 12, 2013 |access-date=December 12, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027154100/http://www.utsystem.edu/news/2013/12/12/board-regents-votes-name-new-ut-south-texas-university-texas-rio-grande-valley |archive-date=2016-10-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

德克萨斯大学大河谷分校是美国以[[拉丁裔美国人|拉丁裔美国人]]學生佔大多數的大学之中規模最大的一所。該校的拉丁裔學生占全校总数的90%，幾乎全都是[[墨西哥裔美国人|墨西哥裔美国人]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.utsystem.edu/sites/utsfiles/documents/strategic-initiatives/fast-facts-2016/fast-facts-2016-06-15.pdf |format=PDF |title=2016 Fast Facts |website=Utsystem.edu |accessdate=2016-09-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822100214/https://www.utsystem.edu/sites/utsfiles/documents/strategic-initiatives/fast-facts-2016/fast-facts-2016-06-15.pdf |archivedate=2016-08-22 }}</ref>

==历史==
2012年12月6日，[[德克薩斯大學系統|德克薩斯大學系統]]批准创办大河谷综合大学以取代[[德州大学布朗思维尔分校|德州大学布朗思维尔分校]]和[[德州大学美洲国家组织分校|德州大学美洲国家组织分校]]。規劃中的新校將開設一所医学院。2013年12月选定校名为德州大河谷大学。<ref>{{cite news |last=Kreighbaum |first=Andrew |title=UT regents approve merging RGV universities, will create medical school |url=http://www.themonitor.com/news/local/article_cec2bf8e-3fd9-11e2-8651-001a4bcf6878.html |accessdate=7 December 2012 |newspaper=[[The_Monitor_(Texas)|The Monitor]] |location=[[McAllen,_Texas|McAllen, Texas]] |date=6 December 2012}}</ref>

[[州長_(美國)|州长]][[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]签署了立法令SB24，批准本校於2013年6月成立。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.capitol.state.tx.us/BillLookup/History.aspx?LegSess=83R&Bill=SB24 |title=Texas Legislature Online - 83(R) History for SB 24 |website=Capitol.state.tx.us |date= |accessdate=2016-09-10 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923200442/http://www.capitol.state.tx.us/BillLookup/History.aspx?LegSess=83R&Bill=SB24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Francisco Fernandez就任该校医学院院长。<ref>{{cite press release |first1=Jenny |last1=LaCoste-Caputo |first2=Karen |last2=Adler |title=Psychiatrist-neuroscientist to be founding dean of UT Rio Grande Valley School of Medicine |url=http://www.utsystem.edu/news/2014/02/14/psychiatrist-neuroscientist-be-founding-dean-ut-rio-grande-valley-school-medicine |accessdate=15 November 2014 |location=Austin, Texas |publisher=The University of Texas System Office of Public Affairs |date=November 6, 2014 |archive-date=2016-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910233650/http://www.utsystem.edu/news/2014/02/14/psychiatrist-neuroscientist-be-founding-dean-ut-rio-grande-valley-school-medicine |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Guy_Bailey|Guy Bailey]]博士被选为第一任校长。<ref>{{cite news |first=Jim |last=Vertuno |title=Guy Bailey named sole finalist for president of The University of Texas Rio Grande Valley |newspaper=[[Lubbock_Avalanche-Journal|Lubbock Avalanche-Journal]] |agency=Associated Press |url=http://lubbockonline.com/education/2014-04-28/guy-bailey-named-sole-finalist-president-university-texas-rio-grande-valley |date=April 28, 2014 |accessdate=April 29, 2014 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220192711/http://lubbockonline.com/education/2014-04-28/guy-bailey-named-sole-finalist-president-university-texas-rio-grande-valley |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年11月德克薩斯大學系統通过了以蓝、绿和橘黄色调的校徽颜色，以及学校的昵称“Vaqueros”。<ref>{{cite press release |first1=Jenny |last1=LaCoste-Caputo |first2=Karen |last2=Adler |title=UT System Board of Regents approves "Vaqueros" as athletic nickname for new university |url=http://www.utsystem.edu/news/2014/11/06/ut-system-board-regents-approves-vaqueros-athletic-nickname-new-university |accessdate=15 November 2014 |publisher=The University of Texas System Office of Public Affairs |location=El Paso, Texas |date=November 6, 2014 |archive-date=2016-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027172150/http://www.utsystem.edu/news/2014/11/06/ut-system-board-regents-approves-vaqueros-athletic-nickname-new-university |dead-url=no }}</ref>

大学的启用仪式于2015年8月31日举行，[[德克薩斯大學系統|德克薩斯大學系統]][[校監|名誉校长]][[威廉·麦克雷文|威廉·麦克雷文]]、[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员[[魯本·伊諾埃薩|魯本·伊諾埃薩]]以及州参议员Juan "Chuy" Hinojosa参加了升旗仪式。<ref name="Rio Grande Guardian">{{cite news |first1=Dayna |last1=Reyes |title=McRaven: UTRGV will change the fabric of the Rio Grande Valley |url=http://riograndeguardian.com/mcraven-utrgv-will-change-the-fabric-of-the-rio-grande-valley/ |date=1 September 2015 |accessdate=2 September 2015 |publisher=Rio Grande Guardian |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115231119/https://riograndeguardian.com/mcraven-utrgv-will-change-the-fabric-of-the-rio-grande-valley/ |archive-date=2018-11-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>名誉校长曾说：“百年之后，德州人回顾今天会说。这是改变德州历史的一天。”<ref name="Rio Grande Guardian"/>

