==学术==
2015年至2016年，德州大河谷大学提供64个学士、49个硕士和4个博士学位課程。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/admissions/why-choose-utrgv/index.htm|title=UTRGV {{!}} Why Choose UTRGV?|website=www.utrgv.edu|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625104846/http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/admissions/why-choose-utrgv/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年有92.7%的學生来自[[卡梅倫縣_(德克薩斯州)|卡梅伦县]]、[[伊達爾戈縣_(德克薩斯州)|伊达哥县]]、[[斯塔爾縣_(德克薩斯州)|斯塔尔县]]和[[威拉西县_(德克萨斯州)|维拉西县]]。2015年秋季学期，西班牙裔学生占88.8%。<ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.utrgv.edu/sair/data-reports/index.htm|title=UTRGV {{!}}  ata and Reports|website=Utrgv.edu|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701034602/http://www.utrgv.edu/sair/data-reports/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

