=== 学术认证 ===
除了从合并前的机构沿袭了所有的学术认证，<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.sacscoc.org/gendisc/56320.pdf|title = Recent Actions taken by SACSCOC Board of Trustees|date = |accessdate = 2015-09-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222163657/http://www.sacscoc.org/gendisc/56320.pdf|archive-date = 2015-12-22|dead-url = yes}}</ref>2016年5月，UTRGV的医学院接受了来自[[Accreditation_Council_for_Graduate_Medical_Education|高等教育医学认证委员会]]（ACGME）的精神病学专科住院实习课程认证，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/about-utrgv/news/press-releases/2016/may-12-utrgv-som-receives-accreditation-for-medical-residency-program-in-psychiatry/index.htm|title=UTRGV {{!}} UTRGV SOM receives accreditation for medical residency program in psychiatry|website=Utrgv.edu|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701042531/http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/about-utrgv/news/press-releases/2016/may-12-utrgv-som-receives-accreditation-for-medical-residency-program-in-psychiatry/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于2016年10月接受了[[Liaison_Committee_on_Medical_Education|Liaison医学教育委员会]]的初步认证。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/about-utrgv/news/press-releases/2015/october-16-lcme-grants-preliminary-accreditation-utrgv-school-of-medicine-now-accepting-applications/|title=UTRGV {{!}} LCME grants preliminary accreditation: UTRGV School of Medicine now accepting applications|website=Utrgv.edu|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701045228/http://www.utrgv.edu/en-us/about-utrgv/news/press-releases/2015/october-16-lcme-grants-preliminary-accreditation-utrgv-school-of-medicine-now-accepting-applications/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

